Class InfoDictionary

  • java.lang.Object

    public final class InfoDictionary
extends java.lang.Object

    Dictionary used in a Metainfo file. This dictionary contains only the required information for this dictionary, as defined in the BTP/1.0 standard.

    • Constructor Detail

      • InfoDictionary

        public InfoDictionary(java.lang.Long length,
                      java.lang.String name,
                      java.lang.Long piece_length,
                      byte[][] pieces)
        Creates a new Info dictionary, holding the required key-values specified in the BTP/1.0 standard.
        Parameters:
        length - Length of the file in bytes.
        name - String containing the name of the file.
        piece_length - An integer indicating the number of bytes in each piece.
        pieces - An array of byte arrays containing the 20-byte SHA1 hash values for all the pieces of the torrent. The hash of the first piece is at index 0.
